strings: <voice_0x01000CC8><se_def>King's Parallelogram: I'll never forget what Sasha said to me.
<voice_0x01000CC9><se_def>King's Parallelogram: It may sound like a pipe dream, but I believe what I see. thank you
<voice_0x01000CCA><se_def>King's Parallelogram: I am also very grateful to Emma. I have finally woken up from this nightmare. Now I can once again be the true king of my people.
<voice_0x01000CCB><se_def>King's Parallelogram: ..... I thank you very much. Please ask if I can help you.
<voice_0x01000CCC><se_def>King's Parallelogram: I promise to do my best to get your money back. Let me know if I can help
<voice_0x01000CCD><se_def>King's Parallelogram: See you then. Have a nice trip. I cannot wait to see you again.
